Class Game

  • java.lang.Object
    • greenfoot.Actor
      • Game
  • public abstract class Game
extends greenfoot.Actor
    Game superclass which will be uses by all subclasses. Spot manager is used in all classes in order to allow gamblers to "attach" themselves to the game.
